      "description": "A dependable budget-friendly vehicle with honest character and plenty of value for the right buyer. This car offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price, making it a smart option for commuting, first-time drivers, or anyone seeking an inexpensive backup vehicle. An affordable opportunity to own a usable vehicle from a trusted seller.",
