      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option that could be just the thing for a first-time driver, a runabout, or a handy little project. It\u2019s been priced to reflect its overall condition, and for the money it offers a lot of practical value. If you want something honest, usable, and easy on the wallet, come take a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Turn-key project with honest cosmetic wear but a strong-running drivetrain and solid fundamentals. The engine pulls cleanly, the transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels planted enough to make this a great budget daily, shop truck, or weekend fixer. Shows its age in the body and interior, but it\u2019s the kind of vehicle you buy for dependable mechanical bones and real usability. If you want something affordable with plenty of service left and room to improve, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
